{"tid":1606894,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"各位香港人，特別係勇武嘅，請入一入嚟","createTime":"2019-09-30T16:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T17:30:55.000Z","uid":218158,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"431aa3d66f02b9592699f69e1081aabd811ec16f","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"我們同為勇武，為的是令香港變得民主，自由，人權，平等，公義，法治。不需再由後代跟魔鬼支共抗爭<br />\n 因此，我們經己作好跟黑警，港共，支共與支持他們的人決一死戰的決心<br />\n以下給各位親愛的香港人：<br />\n吾充吾愛汝之心，助天下人愛其所愛，所以敢先汝而死，不顧汝也。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎各位都留下你哋嘅訣別畀噉多位香港人啦<br />\n但要記住，我哋要喺煲底相擁，珍惜自己嘅生命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港 我愛你</span></span>"},{"pid":"01623f752df9f103874b945d4e7c98610292ec46","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:20.000Z","msg":"101 請出嚟"},{"pid":"2c36c1642036ace188fb3d475d8e5e601473270f","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:26:55.000Z","msg":"香港人 加油"},{"pid":"fc2d0fecfa59d1dd9a22153af2542395455a98fe","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"34794776a5e0c8f47d4d7f8428986615f89a4728","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:38.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"31ceaf397650fbd53811b5f970520122a139033a","tid":1606894,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T16:27:52.000Z","msg":"香港人<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c686662c633e8c5230a226729f450b7329105","tid":1606894,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31ceaf397650fbd53811b5f970520122a139033a"